news: [Community] We made it, the project will reach 1k stars on Github :) In a way it means something, even if there's a lot of other tools that do the same job and in greater ways for some. But surely enough you like jSQL for some reasons if you read this ;) So now we're close to 1k stars it's the moment you speak, tell us what improvements you need, you choose the topic (use Github or @ron190jsql on Twitter, email ron190@ymail.com).
